{"tid":113870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死8隻]8人客貨車轉彎失事　翻側墮河全部死亡","createTime":"2017-02-09T10:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T13:40:52.000Z","uid":32407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"379865a848278d131eab93f5f3adcc974a1d3ec6","tid":113870,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bkncn-20170209074012236-0209_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fbkncn-20170209074012236-0209_05011_001.html&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b10d3e5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bkncn-20170209074012236-0209_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/photo/bkncn-20170209074012236-0209_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170209074012236-0209_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=6e58ad8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河南濮陽縣柳屯鎮肖樓村的342國道上，一輛載有8人的小型客貨車，昨日下午駛至一個彎位時，不慎翻側跌入河溝內，8人最終全數身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，意外後車上其中4人當場死亡，另外4人則在送院後證實不治。目前警方正調查事故原因，並已成立善後處置小組，安撫死者家屬；與此同時，由於事故傷亡人數重大，濮陽市、縣公安部門立即展開交通違法整治，重點對農用車、客貨車進行專項治理。<br />\n<br />\n過到初一,都過唔到十五 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed5776c8323b4b5279b5858417d343f071844b0","tid":113870,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"8個人 冇1個走得出 整撚定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c23df7366ff4dc115aefae17eb04e5135b3f18f","tid":113870,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e29a7c2fe70749c3520bd9f1ee0eee7677fd28","tid":1